==Finnish==
{{Finnish index|kä}}

===Etymology===
Cognates include Estonian ''[[käima]]''.

===Verb===
'''käydä'''

#(''intransitive'') to [[walk]], [[go]] (also of a clock).
#(''intransitive'') to [[visit]].
#(''intransitive'') to [[ferment]], become fermented.
#(''intransitive'') to [[please]], [[suit]], make [[content]].

